Name: WillWalker
About the game: WillWalker is a shooter game set in a cyberpunk universe, where time is your life and you have to kill enemies in order to advance in the game and achieve the objectives. Dive into more than 20 challenging missions which take you through the city and its surroundings, annihilating rival mobs and those who don't want you to succeed. Kill all the enemies, avenge the death of your family and become the next Capo of the city by conquering all of its areas. The time is gold. Do not waste it. MAIN FEATURES Discover and play with 4 unique characters. Upgrade each character to unlock special attacks and weapon upgrades. Kill your enemies and avenge the death of your family. Face the police and gangs to become the new boss of the city. Try to get the best time in each level to get better rewards.
